&lt;h1 id="why-we-may-think"&gt;Why We May Think&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jul 12 2006&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When I was young, I thought the point of the body was to protect the brain. Now I realize it&amp;rsquo;s the other way around. The brain exists to protect the body.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>How to Be an Expert in a Changing World</title><link>https://linguista.cn/paul_graham/essays_en/ecw/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/paul_graham/essays_en/ecw/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;→ &lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/paul_graham/essays_zh/ecw/"&gt;Chinese Version&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
